            <title>[THRIFT-4282] StressTestNonBlocking is disabled in Appveyor as it is unstable on Windows in general</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4282</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have not been able to complete most of my local builds including StressTestNonBlocking because the test fails.  It is disabled in AppVeyor so the builds will pass.  We need this test to be fixed so we can enable it for CI builds again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
